Steelcase - Wikipedia





















 






Steelcase

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Steelcase Inc.





Formerly called

Metal Office Furniture Company



Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: SCS


